<% 
    const faqs = [
    {
        question: "What is Hive?",
        answer: "Hive is a community-driven discussion platform where users can create, join, and engage in discussions within various Buzz Spaces."
    },
    {
        question: "What are Buzz Spaces?",
        answer: "Buzz Spaces, known as Buzz Spaces on our website, use the term instead of Buzz Spaces. They are unique spaces where users can connect and discuss topics of shared interest."
    },
    {
        question: "How do I create a buzz?",
        answer: "To create a buzz, navigate to the Buzz Space of your choice, and click on the 'New Buzz' button. Fill in the title, content, and select relevant tags before submitting your buzz."
    },
    {
        question: "How do I create a Buzz Space?",
        answer: "Creating a Buzz Space is easy. Click on the 'Create Buzz Space' button on the homepage, fill out the necessary details, such as the Buzz Space name, description, and guidelines, to establish your own Buzz Space."
    },
    {
        question: "Can I join multiple Buzz Spaces?",
        answer: "Yes, you can join multiple Buzz Spaces. Explore a diverse range of topics and engage in discussions across different Buzz Spaces based on your interests."
    },
    {
        question: "Can I create multiple Buzz Spaces?",
        answer: "Absolutely! You can create and manage multiple Buzz Spaces on Hive. Each Buzz Space you create becomes a unique space for discussions on specific topics."
    },
    {
        question: "How can I moderate my Buzz Space?",
        answer: "As a Buzz Space creator, you have moderation tools to manage content. You can set Buzz Space guidelines, remove inappropriate content, and appoint moderators to assist in maintaining a positive environment."
    },
    {
        question: "Is there a notification system?",
        answer: "Yes, Hive has a notification system to keep you updated on Buzz Space activities. You'll receive alerts for new buzzs, comments, and Buzz Space announcements."
    },
    {
        question: "Are there privacy settings for my profile?",
        answer: "Yes, you can customize your privacy settings. Control who can see your profile information, buzzs, and interactions based on your preferences."
    },
    {
        question: "How do I report inappropriate content?",
        answer: "If you come across inappropriate content, use the report feature. Reporting helps our moderators review and take necessary actions to maintain a healthy Buzz Space."
    },
    {
        question: "Can I customize the look of my Buzz Space?",
        answer: "Yes, Buzz Space creators can customize the appearance of their Buzz Spaces. Adjust the theme, layout, and other design elements to make your Buzz Space unique."
    }
];


%>


<img class="faq-image" src="assets/FAQ.png" alt="">

<ul class="faq-list">
    <% faqs.forEach(function(faq) { %>
    <li class="faq-item-container">
        <div class="faq-item">
            <p class="question" onclick="faqExpand(this)" >
                <%= faq.question %>
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined faq-expand-btn" >
                    expand_more
                </span>
            </p>
            <p class="answer"><%= faq.answer %></p>
        </div>
    </li>
    <% }); %>
</ul>

<script>
    const faqExpand = (btn) =>{
        btn.closest(".faq-item-container").classList.toggle("expand")
    }
</script>